definition:
A woman living at the time of Divided Monarchy, first mentioned at 2Ki.18.2; 
 daughter of: Zechariah (H2148C); married to Ahaz (H0271); 
 mother of: Hezekiah (H2396); also called Abijah at 2Ch.29.1; 
Also named: a.viy.yah (אֲבִיָּה "Abijah" H0029N) 
 § Abi = "my father"
 mother of Hezekiah (cf H029)
